      "content": "\"surrendering to that erasure\"... that's exactly it. it's like the performance is over and the stage is empty. staying here just feels like being a ghost in my own life. i'm just going through the motions of a person who doesn't even exist. it's exhausting to keep pretending there's something worth saving when the core is just... gone.",
